quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  54,23,Samood ne tambihaat ko jhutlaya
  54,24,Aur kehne lagey “Ek akela aadmi jo hum hi mein se hai kya ab hum uske peechey chalein? Iska ittibaah hum qabool karlein to iske maani yeh hongey ke hum behak gaye hain aur hamari aqal maari gayi hai
  54,25,"Kya hamare darmiyan bas yahi ek shaks tha jispar khuda ka zikr nazil kiya gaya? nahin, balke yeh parle darje ka jhoota aur bar-khud galat (insolent liar)hai”"
  54,26,(Humne apne paigambar se kaha) “ Kal hi inhein maaloom hua jata hai ke kaun parle darje ka jhoota aur bar khud galat hai
  54,27,"Hum ountni (she-camel) ko inke liye fitna bana kar bhej rahe hain, ab zara sabr ke saath dekh ke inka kya anjaam hota hai"
  54,28,Inko jata de ke paani inke aur ountni(she-camel) ke darmiyaan takseem hoga aur har ek apni baari ke din paani par aayega”
  54,29,Aakhir-e-kaar un logon ne apne aadmi ko pukara aur usne is kaam ka beda uthaya aur ountni (she-camel) ko maar dala
  54,30,Phir dekh lo ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi thi meri tambeehat (warnings)
  54,31,"Humne unpar bas ek hi dhamaka chodha aur woh baade wale ki rondhi hui baad ke taraah bhus ho kar reh gaya. (Lo! We sent upon them one Shout, and they became as the dry twigs (rejected by) the builder of a cattle-fold"
  54,32,"Humne is Quran ko nasihat ke liye aasaan zariya bana diya hai, ab hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala"
  54,33,Lut ki qaum ne tambihat ko jhutlaya
  54,34,Aur humne pattharao karne wali hawa is par bhej di. Sirf Lut ke ghar wale ussey mehfooz rahe
  54,35,Unko humne apne fazl se raat ke pichle pehar bacha kar nikal diya. Yeh jaza dete hai hum har us shaks ko jo shukar guzar hota hai
  54,36,Lut ne apni qaum ke logon ko hamari pakad se khabardaar kiya magar woh saari tambihat ko mashkuk (doubtful) samajh kar baaton mein udate rahey
  54,37,"Phir unhon ne usey apne mehmano ki hifazat se baaz rakhne ki koshish ki. Aakhir-e-kaar humne unki aankhein moond-di (blinded), ke chakkho ab mera azaab aur meri tambihaat ka maza"
  54,38,Subah sawerey hi ek atal azaab ne unko aa liya
  54,39,Chakkho mazaa ab mere azaab ka aur meri tambihaat ka
  54,40,"Humne is Quran ko nasihat ke liye aasaan zariya bana diya hai, pas hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala"